25/07/2003
OHRID, Macedonia -- Albania and Macedonia agreed on Thursday (24 July) to boost co-operation in the area of customs administration. Albanian customs head Tatjana Kongoli met in Ohrid with her Macedonian counterpart, Ljubomir Mihajlovski. They discussed co-operation, tax liberalisation, ways of boosting mutual trade, and crime fighting tactics. (MIA, A1 TV - 24/07/03)
